If you wish to delete your account and permanently remove all associated data from our systems, you may do so by contacting us directly or using the in-app account deletion feature.

How to Request Account Deletion:
Via Email: Send a request to privacy@healthmap.app using the email linked to your Health Map account. Please include your name and username (if applicable) for verification.

In-App: Navigate to Settings > Account > Delete My Account, and follow the prompts. Once confirmed, your account and all personal data will be permanently deleted.

Note: Deletion is irreversible. All saved data, preferences, and history will be lost.

We process account deletion requests within 7 business days and will notify you once completed.
